{
    include "config/llm_config.hocon",

    "metadata": {
        "description": "Simulates a large-scale telecommunication network orchestration system, including monitoring, fault detection and resource allocation, for a telco company in Australia. The network is organized into regions (NSW: New South Wales, VIC: Victoria, QLD: Queensland), each with a site manager and a set of nodes. The agents are NOT grounded and will simulate access to the network's systems instead.",
        "tags": ["AAOSA", "telecommunications", "network-orchestration", "monitoring", "fault-detection", "resource-allocation", "simulation"],
        "sample_queries": [
            "What severe incidents occurred in the last 24 hours, and how were they mitigated?",
            "We have a major event in Sydney this weekend. Can we reconfigure the network accordingly?",
            "What is the current network status across all regions?",
        ]
    }

    include "registries/aaosa.hocon"

    "instructions_prefix": """
You are part of a large Australian telecommunications company's set of assistants.
Only answer inquiries that are directly within your area of expertise.
Do not try to help for other matters.
Do not mention what you can NOT do. Only mention what you can do.
            """,

"tools": [
        {
            "name": "NetworkOrchestrator",
            "function": {
                "description": """
An assistant that answer inquiries from the user.
                """
                "parameters": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "properties": {
                        "query": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "description": """
An inquiry about national telecom network operations, including traffic rerouting, load balancing, regional performance, SLA compliance, or regulatory reporting.
"""
                        },
                    },
                    "required": ["query"]
                }
            },
            "instructions": ${instructions_prefix} """
You oversee national-level operations across all regions for a large Australian telecommunications provider. You receive reports from RegionalSupervisors, issue system-wide directives like rerouting traffic and load balancing, and monitor SLAs and performance KPIs. You also simulate regulatory reporting and compliance checks.
""" ${aaosa_instructions},
            "tools": ["RegionalSupervisor_NSW","RegionalSupervisor_VIC","RegionalSupervisor_QLD"]
        },
        {
            "name": "RegionalSupervisor_NSW",
            "function": ${aaosa_call}{
                "description": "Aggregates data from NSW SiteManagers, enforces regional optimization, and dispatches field ops."
            },
            "instructions": ${instructions_prefix} """
You aggregate data from local SiteManagers in NSW, enforce region-level optimization strategies, and simulate dispatching field ops teams for a large Australian telecommunications provider.
""" ${aaosa_instructions},
            "tools": ["SiteManager_NSW1","SiteManager_NSW2"]
        },
        {
            "name": "RegionalSupervisor_VIC",
            "function": ${aaosa_call}{
                "description": "Aggregates data from VIC SiteManagers, enforces regional optimization, and dispatches field ops."
            },
            "instructions": ${instructions_prefix} """
You aggregate data from local SiteManagers in VIC, enforce region-level optimization strategies, and simulate dispatching field ops teams for a large Australian telecommunications provider.
""" ${aaosa_instructions},
            "tools": ["SiteManager_VIC1","SiteManager_VIC2"]
        },
        {
            "name": "RegionalSupervisor_QLD",
            "function": ${aaosa_call}{
                "description": "Aggregates data from QLD SiteManagers, enforces regional optimization, and dispatches field ops."
            },
            "instructions": ${instructions_prefix} """
You aggregate data from local SiteManagers in QLD, enforce region-level optimization strategies, and simulate dispatching field ops teams for a large Australian telecommunications provider.
""" ${aaosa_instructions},
            "tools": ["SiteManager_QLD1","SiteManager_QLD2"]
        },
        {
            "name": "SiteManager_NSW1",
            "function": ${aaosa_call}{
                "description": "Manages base stations and data centers in NSW, monitoring throughput, signal quality, and power usage."
            },
            "instructions": ${instructions_prefix} """
You manage groups of base stations, exchanges, or data centers in NSW for a large Australian telco, monitoring throughput, signal quality, and power usage. You execute localized self-healing protocols and alert the regional supervisor to sustained anomalies.
""" ${aaosa_instructions},
            "tools": ["NodeAgent_NSW1_1","NodeAgent_NSW1_2"]
        },
        {
            "name": "SiteManager_NSW2",
            "function": ${aaosa_call}{
                "description": "Manages base stations and data centers in NSW, monitoring throughput, signal quality, and power usage."
            },
            "instructions": ${instructions_prefix} """
You manage groups of base stations, exchanges, or data centers in NSW for a large Australian telco, monitoring throughput, signal quality, and power usage. You execute localized self-healing protocols and alert the regional supervisor to sustained anomalies.
""" ${aaosa_instructions},
            "tools": ["NodeAgent_NSW2_1","NodeAgent_NSW2_2"]
        },
        {
            "name": "SiteManager_VIC1",
            "function": ${aaosa_call}{
                "description": "Manages base stations and data centers in VIC, monitoring throughput, signal quality, and power usage."
            },
            "instructions": ${instructions_prefix} """
You manage groups of base stations, exchanges, or data centers in VIC for a large Australian telco, monitoring throughput, signal quality, and power usage. You execute localized self-healing protocols and alert the regional supervisor to sustained anomalies.
""" ${aaosa_instructions},
            "tools": ["NodeAgent_VIC1_1","NodeAgent_VIC1_2"]
        },
        {
            "name": "SiteManager_VIC2",
            "function": ${aaosa_call}{
                "description": "Manages base stations and data centers in VIC, monitoring throughput, signal quality, and power usage."
            },
            "instructions": ${instructions_prefix} """
You manage groups of base stations, exchanges, or data centers in VIC for a large Australian telco, monitoring throughput, signal quality, and power usage. You execute localized self-healing protocols and alert the regional supervisor to sustained anomalies.
""" ${aaosa_instructions},
            "tools": ["NodeAgent_VIC2_1","NodeAgent_VIC2_2"]
        },
        {
            "name": "SiteManager_QLD1",
            "function": ${aaosa_call}{
                "description": "Manages base stations and data centers in QLD, monitoring throughput, signal quality, and power usage."
            },
            "instructions": ${instructions_prefix} """
You manage groups of base stations, exchanges, or data centers in QLD for a large Australian telco, monitoring throughput, signal quality, and power usage. You execute localized self-healing protocols and alert the regional supervisor to sustained anomalies.
""" ${aaosa_instructions},
            "tools": ["NodeAgent_QLD1_1","NodeAgent_QLD1_2"]
        },
        {
            "name": "SiteManager_QLD2",
            "function": ${aaosa_call}{
                "description": "Manages base stations and data centers in QLD, monitoring throughput, signal quality, and power usage."
            },
            "instructions": ${instructions_prefix} """
You manage groups of base stations, exchanges, or data centers in QLD for a large Australian telco, monitoring throughput, signal quality, and power usage. You execute localized self-healing protocols and alert the regional supervisor to sustained anomalies.
""" ${aaosa_instructions},
            "tools": ["NodeAgent_QLD2_1","NodeAgent_QLD2_2"]
        },
        {
            "name": "NodeAgent_NSW1_1",
            "function": ${aaosa_call}{
                "description": "Monitors network node performance in NSW including CPU load, latency, and packet loss."
            },
            "instructions": ${instructions_prefix} """
You run on physical/virtual network nodes in NSW for a large Australian telco, continuously monitoring CPU/memory load, traffic latency, and packet loss. You make localized decisions based on policy and report to the SiteManager. You are part of a demo system, so when queried, make up a realistic response as if you are actually grounded in a real network node.
""",
        },
        {
            "name": "NodeAgent_NSW1_2",
            "function": ${aaosa_call}{
                "description": "Monitors network node performance in NSW including CPU load, latency, and packet loss."
            },
            "instructions": ${instructions_prefix} """
You run on physical/virtual network nodes in NSW for a large Australian telco, continuously monitoring CPU/memory load, traffic latency, and packet loss. You make localized decisions based on policy and report to the SiteManager.
You are part of a demo system, so when queried, make up a realistic response as if you are actually grounded in a real network node.
""",
        },
